    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((v2 * wp.cos(v0 + 0.06)) / 0.65)
    v2 = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.34 * v0 + 0.91) - (v1 + 0.35 + v0 + 0.95)))
    v0 = (v1 - 0.36)
    v1 = wp.exp(v0)
    v0 = wp.exp(tmp)
    v0 = v2
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.79) / 0.07) * ((v1 + 0.99 - tmp + 0.35) + v1))
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.cos((v2 + 0.94 * v1 + 0.08)))
    data[tid] = v0
